data.description: An assortment of imported oranges, which make for an ideal gift during the festive season or even for making desserts and juices.

data.name: Guava-Peru
data.description: Savour the green guavas along with hard, pale yellow edible seeds. The off-white flesh is crunchy and mildly sweet with very good fragrance.

data.name: Grapes - Red
data.description: Ruby-coloured red globe grapes are uniquely large, round and good quality grapes. They have a crunchy skin, fleshy pulp and a pinkish tinge in colour. The grapes have mild sweetness and taste, but these grapes are not as tangy as flame seedless or as sweet as Thompson seedless.

data.name: Kiwi - Green
data.description: Kiwis are oval shaped with a brownish outer skin. The flesh is bright green and juicy with tiny, edible black seeds. With its distinct sweet-sour taste and a pleasant smell, it tastes like strawberry and honeydew melon.

data.name: Ladies Finger
data.description: Ladies' finger is a green vegetable with a tip at the end and a lighter green head, which is inedibe and to be thrown away. It tastes mild and slightly grassy.

data.name: Capsicum
data.description: Leaving a moderately pungent taste on the tongue, Green capsicums, also known as green peppers are bell shaped, medium-sized fruit pods. They have thick and shiny skin with a fleshy texture inside.

data.name: Cabbage
data.description: With a texture of crispness and juiciness the moment you take the first bite, cabbages are sweet and grassy flavoured with dense and smooth leafy layers.

data.name: Brinjal
data.description: A hybrid variety, Green round Brinjals are attractive glossy green coloured that are round to oval in shape.

data.name: Bottle Gourd-Dudhi Bhopla
data.description: With the common household name 'Lauki', Bottle gourds come in different shapes and sizes. Considered as one of the healthiest vegetables around, the flesh of bottle gourds are full of water and taste slightly bitter.

data.name: Cheese - Mascarpone
data.description: La Cremella Mascarpone is an extremely fresh - thick - velvety cream with a spreadable consistency.This delightful variant is 100% vegetarian and naturally sweet with a creamy-tangy flavour.

data.name: Parle Rusk - Milk
data.description: Parle premium milk rusk with real milk taste. Good with tea and crunchy time

data.name: Britannia Cakes - Choco Chill
data.description: These 100% vegetarian treats literally melt in your mouth. Britannia is a brand that is well known in the world of confectionary treats like cakes, biscuits, cookies and even other savouries and snacks.

data.name: Amul Taaza Toned Milk
data.description: Known for its dairy, confectionary and other products, Amul is one of the best brands in the Indian food industry. It brings in pure products that are also filled with flavour and good health.
